window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>All evil starts somewhere, and Simon Lewis learns how The Circle - led by Valentine Morgenstern - began. One of 10 adventures in Tales from the Shadowhunter Academy. </p> <p>The Shadowhunter Academy has only just reopened following the disastrous rise of the Circle. Now, the faculty can finally admit to what happened when Valentine was a student. </p> <p>This standalone short story follows the adventures of Simon Lewis, star of the number-one <i>New York Times</i> best-selling series The Mortal Instruments, as he trains to become a Shadowhunter. Tales from the Shadowhunter Academy features characters from Cassandra Clare's <i>Mortal Instruments</i>, <i>Infernal Devices</i>, and the upcoming Dark Artifices and Last Hours series. </p>"; 
